content:
MuleSoft Direct for Health Cloud offers comprehensive integration solutions tailored to fit the healthcare industry needs and use cases of businesses.

Bulk Claims Data Ingestion into Data Cloud: 
Retrieve Medicare Part A, B, and D claims data for the attributed patients.

C-CDA Document Extraction and Ingestion into Data Cloud: 
Extract patient data from the CCDA documents and transform it into Fast Healthcare Interoperability Resources (FHIR) bundles for ingestion into Salesforce Data Cloud.
title: MuleSoft Direct Integrations with Health Cloud
